(81, 7, 1, 'description', 'Paris avec un Parisien : visites guidées à pied du Paris d\'hier et d\'aujourd\'hui. Visites gratuites ; pourboires bienvenus. Toutes nos visites sont exclusivement en anglais.'),
(82, 7, 2, 'description', 'Alex, Agathe, Cécile, and other Paris-born City Guides offer free, intimate, 90 minute walking tours. All major Landmarks, stories (new and old) and local\'s tips on eating / shopping / what to do. It\'s like having a friend in Paris! They know the streets as only a native can and everything happening while you\'re in town. We walk everyday rain or shine, no pre-booking necessary, you just need to show up a the meeting point.\n\n3 tours to choose from :\n\n-PARIS LANDMARKS Right Bank Tour, Paris at its most grandiose and views on the Arc de Triumph, the Champs Elysées the Eiffel Tower and Montmartre. \n \n-NOTRE DAME and the heart of Paris, why Notre Dame is the most visited landmark in Europe? We\'ll tell you everything about the Gargoyles and Quasimodo. \n \n-LATIN QUARTER Left Bank Tour, The medieval Paris, the bohemian and student hang-outs, the place that inspired the greatest artists. \n'),
(83, 7, 3, 'description', 'Paris con un Parisian : tours a pie del Paris de ayer y de hoy. Tours son gratis ; propinas bienvenidas Tours solamente en Inglès.'),
