(870, 77, 2, 'information', '120 artists, artisans... who exhibit our art every Sunday from 10am to 7pm, in front of the tour Montparnasse. \nTo come and meet us : \nMetro: Edgar Quinet  / Bus: 58, 91, 95  / SNCF: Station Paris-Montparnasse\nwww.marchecreation.com - www.paris.fr\nSale:\nVia internet: you can buy any work with the secured Paypal payment. You can directly contact the artist.\nOn location: all major credit cards accepted: visa, mastercard, american express\n'),
